    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/66f41c0158be49d91d380d07daf6feaf.poster.avif?t=1755251245\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/66f41c0158be49d91d380d07daf6feaf.webm?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/66f41c0158be49d91d380d07daf6feaf.mp4?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for <strong>The Karters 2: Turbo Charged</strong>, a fast-paced, action-packed racer built for casual chaos and competitive mastery. With intense multiplayer, deep mechanics, and full modding support available from day one, it’s a karting experience with no speed limit and no limits on creativity.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/383ce09e7630241d0fd7d3a6bbf75857.avif?t=1755251245\" width=1180 height=1470 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/17187da50b8eeea033bd4d823830b995.avif?t=1755251245\" width=1180 height=1566 /></span>  <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/b8149e2ee21700905b69f7283b57abe1.avif?t=1755251245\" width=1180 height=1544 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/3b5d16ffb5defcd0f2fbd3767b576fdc.avif?t=1755251245\" width=1180 height=1464 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Key Features:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Split-Screen  (up to 6 players!) with Split-Screen Online Support</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/709586ffceb3970c9afc671697371775.poster.avif?t=1755251245\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/709586ffceb3970c9afc671697371775.webm?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/709586ffceb3970c9afc671697371775.mp4?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ghost Race with an option to download and share ghost data from Leaderboards</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/cfc3f284a8bf873f95c8db7eb15cc48a.poster.avif?t=1755251245\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/cfc3f284a8bf873f95c8db7eb15cc48a.webm?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/cfc3f284a8bf873f95c8db7eb15cc48a.mp4?t=1755251245\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Steam Workshop support</strong> (1500+ mods already - Tracks, Characters and more)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Integrated Mod Browsing support directly in the game</strong></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Online support with dedicated servers</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Ranked matchmaking support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Single-Player Campaign </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Global Rankings (Leaderboards, Monthly ELO rankings, All-Time ELO Rankings, Tournaments)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 16 official Race Tracks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >6 Battle Arenas</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Team VS Team (online and local) </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Cups with up to 24 rounds (Team VS Team &amp; Online support)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Next Best Ghost option</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >7 Game Modes ( Race, Time Trial, Duo-Time Trial, Battle without time limit, Elimination, Road Breaker, Quick Cut, more to come!)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We are a small indie studio from Poland with a goal to create the best kart racing game on the platform!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2269950/extras/139198e3c5d836ce084256c54b471562.webp?t=1755251245\" width=616 height=50 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p>",
